        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Better Drive Act</b></p> <p>This bill repeals provisions requiring the Department of Transportation to withhold a certain amount of a state's apportionment of federal-aid highway funds if the state fails to enact and enforce a law that requires the revocation or suspension of drivers' licenses of individuals convicted of drug offenses.</p>]]></text>
